SPACE FIGHTER 9000

This is a small game about glory, honor, and space officer's duty.
You are a space squad commander. Unfortunately, all your ships were ambushed and destroyed by evil and ruthless aliens. Your last ship is surrounded without a chance of escaping...
Fight to the end, commander! Take as many of them as you can! Charge!!!

Use WSAD to move and mouse to turn and shoot.

The game is written in JavaScript+HTML5. Just open index.html with your browser.

Sounds are from awesome "The Ur-Quan Masters", and sprites are from here: http://opengameart.org/content/spaceship-set-32x32px

